## Principles

#### Ensure operational readiness & performance

> Proactively define [performance targets](/) (SLOs), test and validate capacity, and continuously optimize
> compute engines to ensure workloads meet business expectations.

#### Automate infrastructure & maintenance

> Eliminate manual operational tasks by codifying all infrastructure, configuration, and data pipelines,
> leveraging Snowflake's built-in automation for scaling and maintenance.

#### Enhance observability & issue resolution

> Gain deep, end-to-end visibility into the platform by capturing and analyzing telemetry, logs, and traces to
> rapidly diagnose and resolve issues.

#### Manage incidents & problems

> Minimize the impact of incidents using AI-driven diagnostics, immutable backups for rapid recovery, and
> automated governance controls.

#### Enable collaboration & Secure Sharing

> Foster a collaborative data culture by establishing a secure, governed internal marketplace for sharing
> data, applications, and models.
